{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we compare FCVAE with an improved frequency-based VAE (FVAE) model, in which the frequency information is integrated into VAE along with the input to reconstruct the original time series.",
    "As depicted in Figure 9(b), FCVAE surpasses FVAE.",
    "This outcome can be attributed to two primary reasons.",
    "Firstly, CVAE, due to its unique architecture that incorporates conditional information, intrinsically outperforms VAE in numerous applications.",
    "Secondly, FVAE does not fully exploit frequency information."
  ]
}